</div>
<div class="video-examples-featured">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="mi869z" data-video-descrip="Upon hearing that one of his henchmen had been stealing the money SPECTRE received from selling Red Chinese drugs in the United States, Ernst Blofeld  executes the guilty henchman by electrocuting him to death in their chair." data-video-title="Blofeld Kills Mook for Theft" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/mi869z_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/mi869z.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/BoardToDeath" data-video-tropename="Board to Death" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="5.00" data-video-rating-count="5" data-video-media-sources="Film/Thunderball" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link featured-widget-vid">
