<h2 class="bold font-l">Blofeld Kills Mook for Theft</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Upon hearing that one of his henchmen had been stealing the money SPECTRE received from selling Red Chinese drugs in the United States, Ernst Blofeld executes the guilty henchman by electrocuting him to death in their chair. </p>
</div>
